sentences.english: Neither of the twins likes dark green.
sentences.chinese: 這對孿生兒誰也不喜歡深綠色。

sentences.english: Pumpkin seeds are dark green seeds also known as pepitas.
sentences.chinese: 南瓜種子是深綠色的種子。

sentences.english: The fruit has dark green pulp which has a delicious flavour like cucumber.
sentences.chinese: 刺角瓜的果肉深綠色，味道鮮美如黃瓜。

sentences.english: The room was carpeted in a very thick green carpet with a wave-like pattern.
sentences.chinese: 這個房間裏鋪着一條帶波浪形花紋的深綠色地毯。

sentences.english: In this image, the mountains are covered in deep green forest.
sentences.chinese: 在這幅圖片中，山嶺爲深綠色的森林覆蓋。

sentences.english: A dark green, round biconvex tablet with opaque coating.
sentences.chinese: 深綠色，圓形不透明塗層雙凸片。

sentences.english: The forest is dark green, while the tundra is still brown.
sentences.chinese: 森林是深綠色，而凍土帶仍然是黃褐色。

sentences.english: Dark green, plain, glossy/ red back.
sentences.chinese: 深綠色波浪圓形葉，葉面光滑，葉背紅。

sentences.english: Dark green is my favorite color.
sentences.chinese: 我喜歡的顏色是深綠色。

sentences.english: He was almost five meters tall and a dark green color.
sentences.chinese: 他幾乎有五米高，呈深綠色。

sentences.english: Flavanoid is the major chemical ingredients in the S. doederleinii.
sentences.chinese: 深綠卷柏的主要化學成分爲黃酮類化合物。

sentences.english: The dark green willow, light gray riverbank.
sentences.chinese: 深綠的河柳，淺灰的河堤。

sentences.english: Dark green is also commonly associated with money.
sentences.chinese: 深綠色還常與金錢聯繫在一起。

sentences.english: Lockers and doors inside here are also painted dark green.
sentences.chinese: 這裏的儲物櫃和門也塗成深綠色。

sentences.english: The necks of the drakes shine like royal green satin4.
sentences.chinese: 一些公鴨脖頸處的羽毛閃着深綠緞面一般的光澤。

sentences.english: Dark green, pointed, glossy/ red back.
sentences.chinese: 深綠色波浪圓形葉，葉面光滑，葉背紅。
